name: Help void TTIP
tagline: Why TTIP is worth moaning about
body:
### TTIP
The **T**ransatlantic **T**rade and **I**nvestment **P**artnership - sometimes called the Transatlantic Free Trade Area (TAFTA) - is a deal draft between the US and Europe currently under negotiation.
